Torrent Power Ltdhas informed BSE that the meeting of the Board of Directors of the Company is scheduled on 10/02/2026 inter alia to consider and approve 1. Unaudited Financial Results for the quarter and nine months ended December 31 2025;

2. Declaration of Interim Dividend to the Equity Shareholders for FY 2025-26 if any;

3. Raising of funds by issuance of Non-Convertible Debentures through Private Placement basis.
